field.textValue:
Raw PacBio reads (HiFi) -> FASTQ format (raw reads);
Assembled contigs per individual -> FASTA format (assemblies, alignments);
VCF (variants) -> VCF format (variant data);
Multiple alignments of sdY-> FASTA format (assemblies, alignments);
Sample metadata (phenotypic sex, population, weight, size, GSI) -> CSV / XLSX formats (metadata, sequencing metrics).
